<refsect1 xml:id='bugs'><title>BUGS</title>
<para><emphasis remap='I'>Rle_skiprow</emphasis>
should not be called when creating an <emphasis remap='I'>RLE</emphasis> file with
<emphasis remap='I'>the_hdr</emphasis>-><emphasis remap='I'>background</emphasis>
set to zero.  The specified number of rows will indeed be skipped, but
they will not be filled with background when the file is read.</para>
</refsect1>
